@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About Gift of the Givers Foundation";
}

<h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>
<p>
    Gift of the Givers Foundation is South Africa's largest disaster relief organization. Our mission is to provide emergency aid and development assistance to those in need. 
    Established in 1992, we have been at the forefront of disaster relief efforts in South Africa and beyond, delivering essential services such as medical care, food, and water.
</p>
<p>
    Our team of dedicated volunteers, medical professionals, and logistics experts work tirelessly to respond to crises swiftly and effectively, ensuring that resources reach those 
    who need them most.
</p>
<p>
    We invite you to join us in making a difference. Whether through donations, volunteering, or spreading awareness, your support is crucial to our mission of bringing hope and 
    relief to communities affected by adversity.
</p>
